mc.server.types

Class TypeMatrixDouble

  • java.lang.Object
    • mc.server.types.TypeMatrixDouble

  • public class TypeMatrixDouble
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a TypeMatrixDouble object.

    Provides methods to read a double matrix, matrix serialization and deserialization methods, and finally standard multiplication methods.

    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Malhar Chaudhari
